  "shortDescription": "Turn any image into a premium puzzle with web search, guide overlay and smooth animated solving.",
  "description": "Puzzle Fuzzle is a premium modern image to puzzle experience built for flow and polish. Import from file or URL, or search the web with live previews, then solve with an adjustable guide overlay, precision snap at least 50 percent overlap with magnet assist, auto rotate, and fully custom difficulty. One tap Solve delivers smooth cinematic animations, while collapsible controls, handy shortcuts, and a theme aware Light and Dark design keep everything effortless. Looking for a refined, stress free puzzle you will return to again and again? Choose Puzzle Fuzzle.",
