    "Web/image import with preview",
    "Guide overlay (opacity)",
    "50% snap + auto-rotate",
    "Custom rows/cols + scatter",
    "One-tap Solve animations",
    "Light/Dark theme, shortcuts",
    "In-app web image search with live preview",
    "Guide overlay toggle + opacity slider",
    "Light/Dark mode with theme-aware backgrounds",
    "Smoother, faster “Solve” for large puzzles",
    "Smarter 50% snap + auto-rotate",
    "Better fullscreen fit + window opacity control",
    "Reliability fixes and performance improvements"
